snippet.title: Tales of Graces F - PS3 - Gameplay Video: Desert Battles
snippet.description:
When crossing a desert full of monster, you can expect some battle.

Tales of Graces F will gain Europe in Summer 2012 on Playstation 3 only.

For more informations about this game, please visit the official Facebook fanpage: http://www.facebook.com/tales or go on your local Namco Bandai Games website: http://www.namcobandaigames.eu/
